column5: Im Wondering if anyone on here has any experience with Moira lake? What's it like hows the fishing, good place to visit? Etc? Any opinions would be good to hear, good or bad..
Walleye is fishing is tough {I've never done well} but apparently can be good and it produces a lot of big muskies by the sounds of it.
The lake is over run with Musky,very good bass and pike fishing.Walleye isn't to bad in the deeper holes.
